name: WestJet 767-338ER [C-FWAD] Close Up Taxi and Takeoff from Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
WestJet's 767 services to London have not gotten off to the best start, with lots of delays due to a number of maintenance issues. Omni Air International subbed a couple of flights recently, and the performance seems to have improved as of late. Anyway, here's fin 672 operating Calgary to Gatwick (on time, for once) taxiing up close and departing runway 35R. ATC is included.

Thanks for watching!
